---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="AI Automation | Ice Cap Labs | Wichita, KS" description="AI automation services for Wichita, Kansas businesses — workflow optimization, chatbots, document processing, reporting, and custom AI tools.">

  <!-- PIXEL HERO -->
  <section class="pixel-hero">
    <h1 class="pixel-hero-title" aria-label="Automate">AUTOMATE</h1>
    <div class="pixel-title-grid" id="pixel-title-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; text-align: center;">
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 700;">
        You Need Automation
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.1" style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Not because it's trendy. Because your competitors are already using it and you're spending 15 hours a week on work a computer could do in 15 minutes.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.2" style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">
        We offer it in all sizes. Simple workflows to AI employees. You don't need to know all the answers. <strong>It's okay to be scared. Frankly, I am too.</strong> This is new for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE OFFER -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-void); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 700;">
        Three Ways We Can Help
      </h2>

      <div style="display: grid; gap: 2rem;">
        <!-- SIMPLE -->
        <div class="reveal" style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Simple Automation</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Email filters. Appointment scheduling. Auto-filing. Social media posting.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">Starts at $1,500 • Saves 5-10 hrs/week</p>
        </div>

        <!-- WORKFLOWS -->
        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.1" style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Multi-Step Workflows</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Lead pipelines. Customer onboarding. Invoice-to-payment. Inventory sync.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">Starts at $3,000 • Saves 10-20 hrs/week</p>
        </div>

        <!-- AI EMPLOYEES -->
        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.2" style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">AI Employees</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Agents that run your social media, track inventory, handle support, coordinate teams.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;">Starts at $8,000 • Saves 20-40+ hrs/week</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.3" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        I use AI employees to run Ice Cap Labs and two other businesses. <a href="/blog/five-weeks-with-openclaw" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline;">Here's how it works.</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BIG CTA -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-deep); padding: 8rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 700px; text-align: center;">
      <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        If you're nervous about the future and don't want to get left behind
      </p>
      
      <a href="/contact" class="reveal giant-cta" data-delay="0.1" style="
        display: inline-block;
        width: 280px;
        height: 280px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, rgba(139,92,246,0.8) 100%);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: white;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139,92,246,0.4);
        margin: 0 auto;
      ">
        Let's Talk
      </a>

      <p class="reveal" data-delay="0.2" style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 2rem;">
        I love talking to people. No pressure. No hard sell. Just a conversation about what you're dealing with and whether automation could help.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QUICK FAQ -->
  <section style="background: var(--bg-void); padding: 6rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 700;">
        Quick Answers
      </h2>

      <div style="display: grid; gap: 1.5rem;">
        <div class="reveal">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">How long to set up?</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">1-2 days for simple. 1-2 weeks for workflows. 2-4 weeks for AI employees.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.05">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">What if it breaks?</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">It escalates to you instead of failing silently. Plus monitoring + alerts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.1">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Will it replace my team?</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Nope. It handles the repetitive 60% so they can focus on the strategic 40%.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" data-delay="0.15">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-primary);">Do I need to be technical?</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">No. You describe the workflow. We build it. We train your team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .giant-cta:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(139,92,246,0.6);
    }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
